        },
        {
            "title": "美股躍升 鮑威爾講話提振9月降息預期",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/hRZd1RGgC3ZeFsCKx8p4WQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/06929f77437e73e4101edb880996458c\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國股市周五上漲，結束了連續五天的下跌。聯儲會主席傑羅姆·鮑威爾的講話導致交易員加大對最早下個月降息的押注。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至紐約時間上午10:48，道瓊工業平均指數上漲1.8%，創下盤中歷史新高，並有望創下自去年12月以來的首次收盤紀錄。標普500指數上漲1.6%，11個板塊全部上漲。以科技股為主的那斯達克100指數上漲1.8%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管在關稅稅率上升的背景下存在對通膨的擔憂，但鮑威爾在懷俄明州傑克遜霍爾講話指出勞動力市場存在風險。受此影響，交易員們迅速加大了對聯儲會最早將在9月會議上放鬆政策、並在年底前進一步降息的押注。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Abound Financial首席投資官David Laut表示：「鮑威爾在傑克遜霍爾的鴿派言論表明，聯儲會已準備好在9月降息，鑒於近期勞動力市場的放緩，這正是投資者希望聽到的消息。」</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/lf_x5PnhZJ8TKCV47decaw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/429a69e2256df689e7824ac37ad659b5\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">股市中風險較高的板塊表現尤為強勁。高盛集團一個跟蹤空頭頭寸最高股票的指數上漲4.2%，而一項衡量尚未盈利公司的指數上漲2.5%。羅素2000指數上漲3.6%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Stocks Surge as Powell Speech Boosts September Rate-Cut Bets</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Jess Menton.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1%E8%BA%8D%E5%8D%87-%E9%AE%91%E5%A8%81%E7%88%BE%E8%AC%9B%E8%A9%B1%E6%8F%90%E6%8C%AF9%E6%9C%88%E9%99%8D%E6%81%AF%E9%A0%90%E6%9C%9F-153440235.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-23 00:30:39",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
